t-b3ebbed\" data-id=\"b3ebbed\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-29ede59 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"29ede59\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"980\" height=\"550\" src=\"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/vince-gx-ZFXbZQaOzeI-unsplash-1024x575.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-11017\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/vince-gx-ZFXbZQaOzeI-unsplash-1024x575.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/vince-gx-ZFXbZQaOzeI-unsplash-300x168.jpg 300w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/vince-gx-ZFXbZQaOzeI-unsplash-768x431.jpg 768w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/vince-gx-ZFXbZQaOzeI-unsplash-1536x862.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/vince-gx-ZFXbZQaOzeI-unsplash-2048x1149.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/vince-gx-ZFXbZQaOzeI-unsplash-802x450.jpg 802w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 980px) 100vw, 980px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d2ba345 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"d2ba345\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f305b9e e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"f305b9e\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a696fee elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a696fee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Highlights:<\/h3>\n<h3><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400;\">Drive through the Middle Atlas Mountains, including cedar forests and Berber villages.<\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Camel trek at sunset into the Sahara Desert.<\/p>\n<p>Experience a night in a traditional Berber camp under the stars.<\/p>\n<p>Explore the Dades Valley and Todra Gorges.<\/p>\n<p><b>3-Day Itinerary<\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>Day 1: Fes to Merzouga<\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>Morning:<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Depart early from Fes.<\/p>\n<p>Drive through Ifrane, known as the &#8220;Switzerland of Morocco.&#8221;<\/p>\n<p>Stop in Azrou to see the cedar forests and Barbary macaques.<\/p>\n<p><b>Afternoon:<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Pass through the Ziz Valley with its lush palm groves.<\/p>\n<p>Arrive in Merzouga by late afternoon.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Evening:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Camel trek into the Sahara Desert at sunset.<\/p>\n<p>Enjoy dinner, music, and storytelling at a traditional Berber camp.<\/p>\n<p>Overnight stay in a desert camp under the stars.<\/p>\n<p><b>Day 2: Merzouga to Dades Valley<\/b><\/p>\n<p><b style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text );\">Morning:<\/b><\/p>\n<div><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text );\">Watch the sunrise over the dunes.<\/span><\/div>\n<div>\n<div><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text );\">Return to Merzouga by camel.<\/span><\/div>\n<div><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text );\">Freshen up and have breakfast before departure.<\/span><\/div>\n<div><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text );\">&nbsp;<\/span><\/div>\n<div>\n<div><b>Highlights:<\/b><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div><b>&nbsp;<\/b><\/div>\n<div>\n<div>Explore the Todra Gorges, famous for its towering rock formations.<\/div>\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n<div>Drive through the Dades Valley, known for its stunning landscapes and &#8220;Monkey Fingers&#8221; rock formations.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div><b>Evening<\/b><\/div>\n<div>\n<p>Overnight stay at a guesthouse or hotel in the Dades Valley.&nbsp;<span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text );\">Dinner included.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Day 3: Dades Valley to Marrakech<\/p>\n<p><b>Morning:<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Drive through the Valley of Roses and the Skoura oasis.<\/p>\n<p>Visit the UNESCO World Heritage site of Ait Ben Haddou, a famous kasbah featured in movies like Gladiator.<\/p>\n<p><b>Afternoon:<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Continue through the High Atlas Mountains via Tizi n\u2019Tichka pass.<\/p>\n<p>Stop for photos and enjoy panoramic views along the way.<\/p>\n<p><b>Evening:<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Arrive in Marrakech by late afternoon or early evening.<\/p>\n<p>Drop-off at your hotel or riad.<\/p>\n<p><\/p>\n<p>&#8212;<\/p>\n<p><b>Inclusions:<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Transportation in a comfortable, air-conditioned vehicle.<\/p>\n<p>English-speaking driver\/guide.<\/p>\n<p>Accommodation in a desert camp and a guesthouse.<\/p>\n<p><b>Camel trek.<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Breakfasts and dinners.<\/p>\n<p><b>Exclusions:<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Lunches and drinks.<\/p>\n<p>Entrance fees to monuments or optional activities.<\/p>\n<p><\/p>\n<p>&#8212;<\/p>\n<p>This 3-day itinerary is ideal for travelers with limited time who want to experience the magic of the Sahara Desert and Morocco&#8217;s diverse landscapes. Let me know if you\u2019d like additional details or booking assistance!<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>3 day tour From Fes to Merzouga Experience the real Morocco with Authentic Berber Travel! This 9-day trip takes you through Morocco&#8217;s rich culture, stunning landscapes, and vibrant cities, starting and ending in Casablanca. Highlights: Drive through the Middle Atlas Mountains, including cedar forests and Berber villages. Camel trek at sunset into the Sahara Desert. [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"parent":11314,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-12689","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/12689","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=12689"}],"version-history":[{"count":10,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/12689\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":12812,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/12689\/revisions\/12812"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11314"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=12689"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}